---
---

<section id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="how">
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="diagram">
          <svg class="wires" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
            <path d="M 90 90 Q 200 130 310 95"></path>
            <path d="M 310 95 Q 340 220 320 330"></path>
            <path d="M 320 330 Q 200 360 110 330"></path>
            <path d="M 110 330 Q 70 200 90 90"></path>
            <path d="M 90 90 L 200 200"></path>
            <path d="M 310 95 L 200 200"></path>
            <path d="M 320 330 L 200 200"></path>
            <path d="M 110 330 L 200 200"></path>
            <circle cx="145" cy="155" r="3"></circle>
            <circle cx="260" cy="160" r="3"></circle>
            <circle cx="260" cy="260" r="3"></circle>
            <circle cx="150" cy="255" r="3"></circle>
          </svg>

          <div class="srv s1">
            <b>hackers.pub</b>
            <span>800 사용자</span>
            <span class="pill">Hackers Pub</span>
          </div>
          <div class="srv s2">
            <b>oeee.cafe</b>
            <span>집계 비공개</span>
            <span class="pill">Oeee</span>
          </div>
          <div class="srv s3">
            <b>kurry.social</b>
            <span>1,935 사용자</span>
            <span class="pill">Mastodon</span>
          </div>
          <div class="srv s4">
            <b>planet.moe</b>
            <span>39,674 사용자</span>
            <span class="pill">Mastodon</span>
          </div>

          <div class="core">
            <div>
              <b>ActivityPub</b>
              공통 프로토콜
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <span class="sec-eyebrow sun">원리</span>
          <h2 class="sec-h">
            작은 서버들이<br /><span class="hl">서로 이어져</span> 있어요.
          </h2>
          <p class="sec-sub">
            각 서버는 독립적으로 운영돼요. 운영자도 규칙도 분위기도 다릅니다. 하지만 <b
              >같은 프로토콜</b
            >을 쓰기 때문에, 한 서버의 계정으로 다른 서버의 사람들을 팔로우하고 답장할 수 있어요.
          </p>

          <ul class="how-points">
            <li>
              <span class="n">01</span>
              <div>
                <b>한 곳에 가입하면 충분</b>
                <p>
                  한 계정으로 다른 서버, 다른 앱(Pixelfed·PeerTube 등)의 사람들과 교류할 수 있어요.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="n lilac">02</span>
              <div>
                <b>서버는 작은 공동체</b>
                <p>관심사나 언어, 분위기가 맞는 곳을 고르면 돼요. 마음에 안 들면 옮기면 됩니다.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="n sun">03</span>
              <div>
                <b>옮겨도 관계가 남아요</b>
                <p>서버 이사 기능이 기본. 팔로우 관계가 함께 따라옵니다.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 56px;
  }
  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .diagram {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .diagram .srv {
    position: absolute;
    width: 120px;
    padding: 14px 14px 12px;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03),
      0 12px 28px -16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .diagram .srv b {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .diagram .srv span {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .diagram .srv .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  }
  .s1 {
    top: 6%;
    left: 6%;
  }
  .s1 .pill {
    background: var(--mint-soft);
    color: var(--mint-deep);
  }
  .s2 {
    top: 10%;
    right: 6%;
  }
  .s2 .pill {
    background: var(--lilac-soft);
    color: var(--lilac-deep);
  }
  .s3 {
    bottom: 10%;
    left: 14%;
  }
  .s3 .pill {
    background: #ffe8d8;
    color: #b54020;
  }
  .s4 {
    bottom: 6%;
    right: 10%;
  }
  .s4 .pill {
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--sun) 35%, white);
    color: #7a5400;
  }

  .core {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    z-index: 3;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(15, 21, 18, 0.4);
  }
  .core b {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    color: white;
  }
  svg.wires {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  svg.wires path {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--ink);
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    stroke-dasharray: 4 5;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }
  svg.wires circle {
    fill: var(--mint-deep);
  }

  .how-points {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .how-points li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .how-points li .n {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--mint-soft);
    color: var(--mint-deep);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .how-points li .n.lilac {
    background: var(--lilac-soft);
    color: var(--lilac-deep);
  }
  .how-points li .n.sun {
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--sun) 35%, white);
    color: #7a5400;
  }
  .how-points li b {
    display: block;
    font-size: 15.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .how-points li p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .how {
      padding: 48px 36px;
    }
    .how-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .how {
      padding: 36px 22px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .diagram {
      max-width: 340px;
    }
    .diagram .srv {
      width: 100px;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .diagram .srv b {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .core {
      width: 110px;
      height: 110px;
    }
    .core b {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
